{"tid":1812221,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"幼貓可放出來玩嗎？","createTime":"2020-01-05T10:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T10:10:04.000Z","uid":64401,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"1dfa39e81f8f667639562a3ea97b61e977801324","tid":1812221,"uid":64401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:15:39.000Z","msg":"貓貓三個月半大，已打左一支針<br />\n<br />\n係咪要打哂三支針先可以放佢出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢不停係到喵喵叫好可憐咁想出黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我怕佢未打哂針，出黎玩完會病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vtuCpkZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvtuCpkZ.png&h=5f19aec2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9smpONL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9smpONL.png&h=65917b77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3nPZUv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3nPZUv.png&h=a5613c7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0be3c702b09cc90930115b683f9f5332de11c0b","tid":1812221,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a431be23eda9c0b6049244f0f57bb18a0925213a","tid":1812221,"uid":109754,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"放啦<br />\n你個籠仲要咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2460e482d334e06abf3b7ed0117fb55c75bd3333","tid":1812221,"uid":258646,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:20:55.000Z","msg":"攞返來未打過針都唔困籠，開心周圍走"},{"pid":"8089c2b0906e28e953a58105dd061de452a7ef1c","tid":1812221,"uid":46741,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:25:17.000Z","msg":